$ser_content = 'a:2:{s:7:"CONTENT";s:0:"";s:4:"VARS";a:2:{s:4:"data";a:11:{i:188;a:25:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"188";s:4:"NAME";s:12:"IVF Programs";s:4:"CODE";s:12:"ivf-programs";s:7:"PICTURE";s:4:"2836";s:11:"DESCRIPTION";s:115:"ART programs (assisted reproductive technologies): IVF, ICSI, frozen embryo transfer and intra-uterine insemination";s:16:"SECTION_PAGE_URL";s:23:"/services/ivf-programs/";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:16:"DESCRIPTION_TYPE";s:4:"html";s:11:"EXTERNAL_ID";s:0:"";s:14:"IBLOCK_TYPE_ID";s:11:"services_en";s:11:"IBLOCK_CODE";s:8:"services";s:18:"IBLOCK_EXTERNAL_ID";s:0:"";s:13:"GLOBAL_ACTIVE";s:1:"Y";s:4:"SORT";s:2:"10";s:7:"UF_ICON";s:6:"menu-1";s:15:"UF_SHOW_ON_MAIN";s:1:"1";s:17:"UF_SHOW_ON_PRICES";s:1:"1";s:8:"UF_VIDEO";N;s:20:"UF_SHOW_TYPES_PRICES";s:1:"0";s:14:"UF_DESCRIPTION";s:2367:"&lt;p&gt;According to&nbsp;the statistic data, about one couple of&nbsp;seven has to&nbsp;consider IVF as&nbsp;the only way to&nbsp;conceive a&nbsp;child. During the procedure, an&nbsp;egg is&nbsp;fertilized with sperm in&nbsp;the laboratory. Then an&nbsp;embryo is&nbsp;transferred into the woman&rsquo;s uterine cavity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Current technologies help to&nbsp;increase success rates in&nbsp;the IVF treatment programs in&nbsp;some cases up&nbsp;to&nbsp;50% and more. Chances are higher in&nbsp;women under 35. In&nbsp;any case, the procedure is&nbsp;safe and can be&nbsp;repeated many times until the wished result is&nbsp;achieved.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;In&nbsp;what cases is&nbsp;IVF indicated?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The procedure is&nbsp;indicated if&nbsp;there is&nbsp;no&nbsp;other way to&nbsp;treat infertility:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;non-patent fallopian tubes due to&nbsp;their pathology;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;no&nbsp;fallopian tubes;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;no&nbsp;ovulation or&nbsp;small number of&nbsp;eggs and their low quality;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;no&nbsp;uterus or&nbsp;ovaries;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;small number of&nbsp;motile or&nbsp;morphologically normal sperm in&nbsp;a&nbsp;male partner;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;confirmed endometriosis;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;sexual disorders that prevent conception.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;IVF is&nbsp;also possible in&nbsp;the case of&nbsp;serious hereditary diseases in&nbsp;the history: during the treatment program the embryos will be&nbsp;tested and only healthy embryos will be&nbsp;transferred into the uterine cavity.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Where to&nbsp;do&nbsp;IVF in&nbsp;Saint-Petersburg?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;IVF is&nbsp;just one infertility treatment program. Our International Centre for Reproductive Medicine (ICRM) practices different methods and technologies: stimulated and natural cycle IVF, ICSI, PGT, assisted hatching and other procedures. The key to&nbsp;success is&nbsp;having full information. Before the treatment program, the doctor will administer a&nbsp;number of&nbsp;tests for both partners. Based on&nbsp;the data received, the specialist will determine what treatment program will fit your needs best to&nbsp;help you conceive and give birth to&nbsp;the baby, and will inform you of&nbsp;the costs of&nbsp;your treatment.&lt;/p&gt;";s:13:"actions_count";i:0;s:10:"prices_url";s:40:"/prices-and-actions/prices/#ivf-programs";s:7:"picture";a:10:{s:8:"ORIGINAL";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:13:"webp_ORIGINAL";s:49:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/0_0_1_95/eco.webp";s:12:"main_complex";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:17:"webp_main_complex";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/114_114_1_95/eco.webp";s:14:"services_index";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:19:"webp_services_index";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/114_114_1_95/eco.webp";s:8:"category";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:13:"webp_category";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/114_114_1_95/eco.webp";s:6:"prices";s:26:"/upload/iblock/079/eco.png";s:11:"webp_prices";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/079/114_114_1_95/eco.webp";}s:24:"showServiceTypesOnPrices";b:0;s:8:"services";a:14:{i:3931;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3931";s:4:"NAME";s:20:"Stimulated Cycle IVF";s:4:"CODE";s:20:"stimulated-cycle-ivf";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:37:"IVF with hormonal ovarian stimulation";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:847:"<h3>How much is&nbsp;a&nbsp;stimulated cycle IVF?</h3>
<p>
	 The procedure includes:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>ultrasound scans to&nbsp;monitor growth of&nbsp;follicles and endometrium condition;</li>
	<li>ovarian puncture and eggs retrieval (including intravenous anesthesia);</li>
	<li>eggs fertilization;</li>
	<li>embryo culture;</li>
	<li>embryo transfer;</li>
	<li>post-transfer medical support (after the transfer of&nbsp;embryos into the uterine cavity);</li>
	<li>pregnancy test;</li>
</ul>
<p>
	 In&nbsp;average, the amount needed for stimulation drugs is&nbsp;approximately 50,000 rubles per one IVF cycle. The amount will differ in&nbsp;every case because the list of&nbsp;medications and their dosages are determined by&nbsp;a&nbsp;doctor individually based on&nbsp;the patient’s history and her pre-treatment test results.
</p>";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:44:"/services/ivf-programs/stimulated-cycle-ivf/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"188";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:323:"&lt;p&gt;The chances for pregnancy in&nbsp;an&nbsp;IVF program are higher when several eggs are used, preferably 8-10 of&nbsp;them. A&nbsp;woman can produce only one follicle, i.e. one egg, in&nbsp;a&nbsp;natural menstrual cycle. That is&nbsp;why doctors often use hormonal ovarian stimulation in&nbsp;IVF cycles.&lt;/p&gt;";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}s:31:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3931:428";s:21:"PROPERTY_STAGES_VALUE";a:8:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:75:"Hormonal ovarian stimulation to grow several follicles (duration 9-14 days)";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:113:"Ultrasound scans to monitor growth of follicles and endometrium condition during the hormonal ovarian stimulation";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:128:"Ovarian puncture and eggs retrieval under general intravenous anesthesia (usually performed on day 11-16 of the menstrual cycle)";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:3;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:64:"Sperm collection for fertilization on the day of eggs retrieval ";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:4;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:102:"Eggs fertilization with the partner\'s sperm in the laboratory (performed on the day of eggs retrieval)";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:5;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:51:"Embryos culture in the laboratory (during 3-6 days)";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:6;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:58:"Transfer of 1-2 embryos into the patient\'s uterine cavity ";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:7;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:56:"Pregnancy test (made on day 12-14 after embryo transfer)";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}}s:26:"PROPERTY_SPECIALISTS_VALUE";a:7:{i:0;s:2:"50";i:1;s:2:"28";i:2;s:2:"63";i:3;s:2:"65";i:4;s:1:"4";i:5;s:2:"55";i:6;s:2:"10";}s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE";s:11:"169 000 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3931:431";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";s:28:"Medications are not inc