291;O:31:"Mcrm\\Model\\Services\\ServiceType":12:{s:7:"appends";a:1:{i:0;s:14:"priceFormatted";}s:21:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'sectionsAreFetched";b:0;s:24:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'fieldsSelectedForSave";a:0:{}s:14:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'eventErrors";a:0:{}s:19:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'fieldsAreFetched";b:1;s:2:"id";s:5:"46291";s:6:"fields";a:10:{s:2:"ID";s:5:"46291";s:4:"NAME";s:15:"Embryo transfer";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:0:"";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"91";s:20:"PROPERTY_PRICE_VALUE";s:10:"26 000 ₽";s:23:"PROPERTY_PRICE_VALUE_ID";s:9:"46291:439";s:32:"PROPERTY_PRICE_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:35:"PROPERTY_PRICE_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:9:"46291:440";s:4:"SORT";s:3:"500";s:17:"PREVIEW_TEXT_TYPE";s:4:"text";}s:11:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'original";a:10:{s:2:"ID";s:5:"46291";s:4:"NAME";s:15:"Embryo transfer";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:0:"";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"91";s:20:"PROPERTY_PRICE_VALUE";s:10:"26 000 ₽";s:23:"PROPERTY_PRICE_VALUE_ID";s:9:"46291:439";s:32:"PROPERTY_PRICE_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:35:"PROPERTY_PRICE_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:9:"46291:440";s:4:"SORT";s:3:"500";s:17:"PREVIEW_TEXT_TYPE";s:4:"text";}s:20:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'languageAccessors";a:0:{}s:7:"related";a:0:{}s:9:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'hidden";a:0:{}s:10:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'visible";a:0:{}}}}s:6:"action";b:0;}i:3930;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3930";s:4:"NAME";s:17:"Natural Cycle IVF";s:4:"CODE";s:17:"natural-cycle-ivf";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:40:"IVF without hormonal ovarian stimulation";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:2621:"<h2>Medical indications for Natural Cycle IVF</h2>
<p>
	 The protocol is&nbsp;usually recommended to&nbsp;a&nbsp;patient&nbsp;if:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>she has negative experience of&nbsp;hormonal therapy;</li>
	<li>her response to&nbsp;hormonal stimulation is&nbsp;very poor;</li>
	<li>her IVF failures were due to&nbsp;implantation problems;</li>
	<li>even when stimulated her ovaries produce 1-3&nbsp;oocytes.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	 To&nbsp;understand what stages will be&nbsp;included into the procedure, it&nbsp;is&nbsp;important to&nbsp;know your treatment program:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>Conventional IVF: ultrasound scans to&nbsp;monitor growth of&nbsp;the follicle and endometrium condition, ovarian puncture and the oocyte retrieval, fertilization using standard IVF method and embryo culture, its transfer into the uterine cavity.</li>
	<li>IVF without embryo transfer: ultrasound scans to&nbsp;monitor growth of&nbsp;the follicle, ovarian puncture and the oocyte retrieval. After that, either oocyte freezing is&nbsp;done or&nbsp;oocyte fertilization and embryo culture followed by embryo freezing.</li>
	<li>Fertilization using ICSI (Intracytoplasmic Sperm Injection) method: ultrasound scans to&nbsp;monitor growth of&nbsp;the follicle and endometrium condition, ovarian puncture and the oocyte retrieval, fertilization using ICSI method and embryo culture, its transfer into the uterine cavity.</li>
	<ul>
		<p>
			 The mandatory stage of&nbsp;every natural cycle IVF is&nbsp;observation (monitoring) of&nbsp;the follicle growth and maturation in&nbsp;the ovary. For this, a&nbsp;fertility specialist uses ultrasound scans. The procedure is&nbsp;usually performed every 2-3&nbsp;days.
		</p>
		<p>
			 When the follicle achieves a&nbsp;certain size, usually in&nbsp;the middle of&nbsp;the menstrual cycle, a&nbsp;HCG (human chorionic gonadotropin) or&nbsp;a&nbsp;GnRH agonist (gonadotropin-releasing hormone agonist) injection is&nbsp;administered. It&nbsp;is&nbsp;necessary for final maturation of&nbsp;the oocyte and its fertilization.
		</p>
		<p>
			 In&nbsp;34-36 hours after the injection, an&nbsp;ovarian puncture and the oocyte retrieval is&nbsp;scheduled. After the special treatment in&nbsp;the laboratory, the oocyte is&nbsp;fertilized using a&nbsp;standard IVF procedure or&nbsp;ICSI.
		</p>
		<p>
			 In&nbsp;the laboratory, the embryo is&nbsp;cultured&nbsp;— it&nbsp;is&nbsp;developing in&nbsp;a&nbsp;special incubator. 3-5 days after the oocyte retrieval the embryo goes back to&nbsp;the woman’s body, it&nbsp;is&nbsp;transferred to&nbsp;the uterine cavity.
		</p>
	</ul>
</ul>";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:41:"/services/ivf-programs/natural-cycle-ivf/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"188";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:756:"&lt;p&gt;Natural cycle IVF does not employ any stimulation protocols. The advantages of&nbsp;the method are the following:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;low risk of&nbsp;multiple pregnancy;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;as&nbsp;a&nbsp;rule, no&nbsp;general anesthesia is&nbsp;required during ovarian puncture;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;no&nbsp;risk of&nbsp;ovarian hyperstimulation syndrome;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;less expensive procedure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At&nbsp;the same time, in&nbsp;natural cycle IVF programs, pregnancy rates are much lower comparing to&nbsp;stimulated cycle IVF, there is&nbsp;a&nbsp;high risk of&nbsp;treatment cancellation due to&nbsp;premature ovulation, no&nbsp;follicle growth or&nbsp;low egg quality.&lt;/p&gt;";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}s:31:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:428";s:21:"PROPERTY_STAGES_VALUE";a:8:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:87:"Ultrasound scans to monitor growth of the follicle, ovulation and endometrium condition";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:16:"LH level control";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:84:"Ovarian puncture and eggs retrieval (usually without intravenous general anesthesia)";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:3;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:51:"Your partner’s sperm collection for fertilization";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:4;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:35:"Egg fertilization at the laboratory";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:5;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:14:"Embryo culture";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:6;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:46:"Transfer of the embryo into the uterine cavity";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:7;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:14:"Pregnancy test";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}}s:26:"PROPERTY_SPECIALISTS_VALUE";a:7:{i:0;s:2:"50";i:1;s:2:"28";i:2;s:2:"63";i:3;s:2:"65";i:4;s:1:"4";i:5;s:2:"55";i:6;s:2:"10";}s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE";s:11:"121 000 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:431";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";s:28:"Medications are not included";s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:432";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:433";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:434";s:23:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE";N;s:26:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:435";s:29:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE";N;s:32:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:436";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:437";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:438";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:591";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:592";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:593";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:594";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:595";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:596";s:33:"PROPERTY_HIDE_PRICE_TOOLTIP_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_HIDE_PRICE_TOOLTIP_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:621";s:20:"PROPERTY_TEXT1_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:913:"&lt;p&gt;It&nbsp;is&nbsp;important to&nbsp;be&nbsp;careful during the next 12-14 days after the embryo transfer (post-transfer period):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;eat well, drink enough;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;try to&nbsp;rest more;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;do&nbsp;not worry, try to&nbsp;avoid any stress;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;avoid saunas and swimming pools;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;do&nbsp;not take hot baths;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;avoid intensive physical exercises and sport;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;avoid sex contacts;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;take all drugs as&nbsp;prescribed by&nbsp;your doctor.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;12-14 days after the embryo transfer, a&nbsp;pregnancy test is&nbsp;done to&nbsp;check if&nbsp;implantation of&nbsp;the embryo into the uterine lining happened. If&nbsp;the pregnancy test is&nbsp;positive, ultrasound scan is&nbsp;done on&nbsp;day 21.&lt;/p&gt;
";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}s:26:"PROPERTY_TEXT1_DESCRIPTION";s:0:"";s:23:"PROPERTY_TEXT1_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:627";s:20:"PROPERTY_TEXT2_VALUE";b:0;s:26:"PROPERTY_TEXT2_DESCRIPTION";N;s:23:"PROPERTY_TEXT2_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3930:628";s:20:"PROPERTY_TEXT3_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:430:"&lt;p&gt;Contraindications to&nbsp;Natural Cycle IVF:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Acute inflammatory processes in&nbsp;a&nbsp;patient&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Irregular menstrual cycle, natural ovulation does not occur&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Lumps and malignant tumors&lt;/li&gt;
