ltations provided by doctors of ART Department and Outpatient Department";s:16:"SECTION_PAGE_URL";s:24:"/services/consultations/";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:16:"DESCRIPTION_TYPE";s:4:"html";s:11:"EXTERNAL_ID";s:0:"";s:14:"IBLOCK_TYPE_ID";s:11:"services_en";s:11:"IBLOCK_CODE";s:8:"services";s:18:"IBLOCK_EXTERNAL_ID";s:0:"";s:13:"GLOBAL_ACTIVE";s:1:"Y";s:4:"SORT";s:2:"15";s:7:"UF_ICON";s:6:"menu-2";s:15:"UF_SHOW_ON_MAIN";s:1:"0";s:17:"UF_SHOW_ON_PRICES";s:1:"0";s:8:"UF_VIDEO";N;s:20:"UF_SHOW_TYPES_PRICES";s:1:"0";s:14:"UF_DESCRIPTION";s:1389:"&lt;p&gt;ICRM offers consultations of&nbsp;the following specialists:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;fertility specialists;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;gynecologists and obstetricians-gynecologists;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;urologists;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;endocrinologists;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;hematologist&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;genetic counselors;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;psychologists;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;oncologists;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;internists.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&nbsp;also offer joint consultations of&nbsp;a&nbsp;fertility specialist with Professor Vladislav Korsak, D.Sc., obstetrician-gynecologist of&nbsp;the highest category.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Advantages of&nbsp;consultations provided by&nbsp;ICRM specialists&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A&nbsp;team of&nbsp;highly skilled medical specialists work in&nbsp;our Centre. Thanks to&nbsp;them, we&nbsp;can guarantee our patients:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;individual approach;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;professional conclusions;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;expert opinions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our doctors can talk to&nbsp;you offline and online.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please use our website to&nbsp;find out the schedule of&nbsp;work of&nbsp;our doctors or&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;#contactus&quot; data-modal-open=&quot;&quot;&gt;contact&lt;/a&gt; our International Manager.&lt;/p&gt;";s:13:"actions_count";i:0;s:10:"prices_url";s:41:"/prices-and-actions/prices/#consultations";s:7:"picture";a:10:{s:8:"ORIGINAL";s:30:"/upload/iblock/a99/consult.png";s:13:"webp_ORIGINAL";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/a99/0_0_1_95/consult.webp";s:12:"main_complex";s:30:"/upload/iblock/a99/consult.png";s:17:"webp_main_complex";s:57:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/a99/114_114_1_95/consult.webp";s:14:"services_index";s:30:"/upload/iblock/a99/consult.png";s:19:"webp_services_index";s:57:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/a99/114_114_1_95/consult.webp";s:8:"category";s:30:"/upload/iblock/a99/consult.png";s:13:"webp_category";s:57:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/a99/114_114_1_95/consult.webp";s:6:"prices";s:30:"/upload/iblock/a99/consult.png";s:11:"webp_prices";s:57:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/a99/114_114_1_95/consult.webp";}s:24:"showServiceTypesOnPrices";b:0;s:8:"services";a:12:{i:3942;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3942";s:4:"NAME";s:33:"Fertility Specialist Consultation";s:4:"CODE";s:33:"fertility-specialist-consultation";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:0:"";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:2589:"<p>
	 If&nbsp;you cannot get pregnant despite having regular unprotected sex for a&nbsp;year, if&nbsp;you are planning a&nbsp;family and had miscarriages before, it&nbsp;is&nbsp;time to&nbsp;see a&nbsp;fertility specialist.
</p>
<p>
	 You can make an&nbsp;appointment by&nbsp;phone, by&nbsp;sending an&nbsp;enquiry to&nbsp;our International Manager at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:trukhina@mcrm.ru">trukhina@mcrm.ru</a>, or&nbsp;by&nbsp;using our <a href="#contactus" data-modal-open="">contact form</a>. Please, prepare for your first appointment. Try to&nbsp;remember and, if&nbsp;necessary, write down information about possible inherited and chronic diseases, illnesses and surgeries you might have had before, complete our <a href="/upload/docs/questionnaire_for_first_visit.pdf">Questionnaire for the first visit</a>. This will help our doctor to&nbsp;get a&nbsp;full picture of&nbsp;your health and find the best treatment for you faster. Our Fertility Specialist will ask questions to&nbsp;complete your case history, please answer sincerely about your health and your sexual life. Yours answers may influence the strategy of&nbsp;your examination and treatment.
</p>
<p>
	 It&nbsp;makes sense for both partners to&nbsp;start <a href="/upload/docs/patients_guide.pdf">pre-treatment examination</a>, this will help to&nbsp;achieve your goals in&nbsp;a&nbsp;shorter time. In&nbsp;ICRM, you can get consultations of&nbsp;a&nbsp;<a href="/services/consultations/gynecological-consultation/">Gynecologist</a>, <a href="/services/consultations/urology-consultation/">Urologist-Andrologist</a>, <a href="/services/consultations/endocrinology-consultation/">Endocrinologist</a>, <a href="/services/consultations/genetic-counseling/">Genetic Counselor</a>, and do&nbsp;all necessary tests. If&nbsp;you have any recent test results or&nbsp;relevant conclusions of&nbsp;medical specialists, please, remember to&nbsp;bring a&nbsp;copy. This will help to&nbsp;save your time and money.
</p>
<p>
	 Based on&nbsp;pre-treatment examination results, our Fertility Specialist will choose the best treatment strategy for you, suggest the most effective way to&nbsp;overcome infertility and/or recurrent miscarriages (including intra-uterine insemination, IVF, ICSI, egg or&nbsp;sperm donation, etc.)
</p>
<p>
	 You can contact one of&nbsp;our Fertility Specialist using a&nbsp;<a href="#contactus" data-modal-open="">contact form</a> or&nbsp;through online consultation. However, please, remember that an&nbsp;online consultation cannot be&nbsp;equal to&nbsp;actually seeing a&nbsp;doctor.
