47;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3947";s:4:"NAME";s:26:"Endocrinology Consultation";s:4:"CODE";s:26:"endocrinology-consultation";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:0:"";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:989:"<p>
	 Dr. Elena Soboleva, ICRM endoctinologist, DSc.Medicine, is a highy qualified specialist of the expert level. Her professional area is diagnostics and treatment of the diseases that are at the meeting point of two specializations: endocrinology and gynecology (menstrual cycle disorders, hyperandrogenism, infertility, recurrent miscarriages, menopausal syndrome). She also corrects various endocrine disorders (thyroid, adrenal, pituitary, diabetes mellitus type 2) including those in patients both planning and carrying pregnancy. Much attention is paid to obesity management both in men and in women.
</p>
<p>
	 To&nbsp;make an&nbsp;appointment please call&nbsp;us or&nbsp;complete our contact form. You can also contact one of&nbsp;our specialists using the <a href="#contactus" data-modal-open="">contact form</a> or&nbsp;through online consultation. However, please, remember that an&nbsp;online consultation cannot be&nbsp;equal to&nbsp;actually seeing a&nbsp;doctor.
