ed";N;s:18:"price3OldFormatted";b:0;s:15:"price4Formatted";N;s:18:"price4OldFormatted";b:0;s:8:"currency";b:0;s:5:"text1";s:0:"";s:5:"text2";s:0:"";s:5:"text3";s:0:"";s:10:"advantages";a:0:{}s:13:"disadvantages";a:0:{}s:12:"serviceTypes";O:29:"Illuminate\\Support\\Collection":1:{s:8:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'items";a:0:{}}s:6:"action";b:0;}i:3945;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3945";s:4:"NAME";s:18:"Genetic Counseling";s:4:"CODE";s:18:"genetic-counseling";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:0:"";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:2317:"<p>
	 If&nbsp;you want to&nbsp;know if&nbsp;there is&nbsp;a&nbsp;risk of&nbsp;transmitting a&nbsp;hereditary disease to&nbsp;you future children, you have an&nbsp;opportunity to&nbsp;visit our Genetic Counselor. Genetic counselling may be&nbsp;useful both at&nbsp;the stage of&nbsp;family planning and during your pregnancy.
</p>
<p>
	 We&nbsp;recommend making an&nbsp;appointment with our Genetic Counselor in&nbsp;the following cases:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>Reasons for infertility in&nbsp;your couple are not known.</li>
	<li>Two and more miscarriages or&nbsp;missed miscarriages in&nbsp;the history.</li>
	<li>A&nbsp;woman in&nbsp;the couple is&nbsp;over 35.</li>
	<li>In&nbsp;your family, there is&nbsp;a&nbsp;child or&nbsp;a&nbsp;relative with a&nbsp;hereditary disease or&nbsp;congenital abnormalities.</li>
	<li>Future parents are close relatives.</li>
	<li>A&nbsp;woman had a&nbsp;disease, took drugs that could have negative influence on&nbsp;the fetus, was exposed to&nbsp;radiation or&nbsp;toxic agents in&nbsp;the menstrual cycle, in&nbsp;which the conception occurred, or&nbsp;during her pregnancy.</li>
	<li>Abnormalities revealed at&nbsp;ultrasound screens during pregnancy.</li>
	<li>Screening revealed high or&nbsp;borderline risk of&nbsp;chromosomal defect in&nbsp;a&nbsp;fetus.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	 Please, use our <a href="#contactus" data-modal-open="">contact form</a> to&nbsp;make an&nbsp;appointment. Our International Manager will contact you to&nbsp;offer convenient date and time.
</p>
<p>
	 During the consultation, our Genetic Counselor will ask questions about your health and way of&nbsp;life as&nbsp;well as&nbsp;possible inherited diseases in&nbsp;your family. The doctor will estimate potential risk of&nbsp;congenital defects in&nbsp;a&nbsp;fetus taking into consideration mother and father’s medical background. If&nbsp;necessary, you will be&nbsp;referred for&nbsp;genetic screenings. In&nbsp;ICRM, you can also do&nbsp;pre-implantation genetic testing of&nbsp;the embryos received after IVF treatment program to&nbsp;detect possible gene and chromosomal defects.
</p>
<p>
	 You can also make an&nbsp;appointment for the online consultation. However, please, remember that an&nbsp;online consultation cannot be&nbsp;equal to&nbsp;actually seeing a&nbsp;doctor.
</p>";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:43:"/services/consultations/genetic-counseling/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"187";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";b:0;s:31:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:428";s:21:"PROPERTY_STAGES_VALUE";a:6:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:32:"Completing detailed case history";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:41:"Completing hereditary history (genealogy)";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:97:"Physical examination of&nbsp;the couple (to&nbsp;assess possible external dysembryogenic stigmas)";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:3;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:75:"Evaluation of&nbsp;the laboratory results if&nbsp;any of&nbsp;them provided";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:4;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:28:"Making preliminary diagnosis";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:5;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:55:"Referring for further screening tests if&nbsp;necessary";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}}s:26:"PROPERTY_SPECIALISTS_VALUE";a:1:{i:0;s:2:"11";}s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE";s:9:"3 500 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:431";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";s:7:"Initial";s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:432";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE";s:9:"2 900 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:433";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";s:7:"Further";s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:434";s:23:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE";N;s:26:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:435";s:29:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE";N;s:32:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:436";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:437";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:438";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:591";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3945:592";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION