N;s:18:"price4OldFormatted";b:0;s:8:"currency";b:0;s:5:"text1";s:0:"";s:5:"text2";s:0:"";s:5:"text3";s:0:"";s:10:"advantages";a:0:{}s:13:"disadvantages";a:0:{}s:12:"serviceTypes";O:29:"Illuminate\\Support\\Collection":1:{s:8:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'items";a:0:{}}s:6:"action";b:0;}i:3941;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3941";s:4:"NAME";s:30:"Internal Medicine Consultation";s:4:"CODE";s:30:"internal-medicine-consultation";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:0:"";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:2048:"<p>
	 Internal Medicine Consultation may be&nbsp;required not only when you have complaints but also for the purpose of&nbsp;prevention and early stage diagnosis of&nbsp;various conditions.
</p>
<p>
	 You can make an&nbsp;appointment with an&nbsp;internist in&nbsp;a&nbsp;case you are not sure, which narrow specialist is&nbsp;appropriate to&nbsp;address in&nbsp;your case. You may also be&nbsp;referred to&nbsp;an&nbsp;internist by&nbsp;other specialists such as&nbsp;a&nbsp;<a href="/services/consultations/gynecological-consultation/">gynecologist</a>, a&nbsp;<a href="/services/consultations/urology-consultation/">urologist-andrologist</a>, an&nbsp;<a href="/services/consultations/endocrinology-consultation/">endocrinologist</a>. An&nbsp;internist’s conclusion is&nbsp;required if&nbsp;you undergo medical examination for infertility or&nbsp;family planning, if&nbsp;you prepare for IVF or&nbsp;any surgical treatment. In&nbsp;addition, regular check-ups by&nbsp;an&nbsp;internist are necessary for all pregnant women.
</p>
<p>
	 The doctor will listen to&nbsp;your complaints, ask questions about your medical, hereditary history, your way of&nbsp;living and possible previous diseases. After that, the doctor will examine your full body, listen to&nbsp;your heart and lungs, check your blood pressure.
</p>
<p>
	 For the Internal Medicine Consultation, please bring any recent laboratory and/or instrumental test results as&nbsp;well as&nbsp;written conclusions made by&nbsp;other medical specialists. If&nbsp;necessary, our doctor will refer you for additional tests or&nbsp;for consultations with other narrow specialists.
</p>
<p>
	 Please, use our <a href="#contactus" data-modal-open="">contact form</a> to&nbsp;make an&nbsp;appointment. Our International Manager will contact you to&nbsp;offer convenient date and time. You can also make an&nbsp;appointment for the online consultation. However, please, remember that an&nbsp;online consultation cannot be&nbsp;equal to&nbsp;actually seeing a&nbsp;doctor.
</p>
