ges";a:0:{}s:13:"disadvantages";a:0:{}s:12:"serviceTypes";O:29:"Illuminate\\Support\\Collection":1:{s:8:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'items";a:0:{}}s:6:"action";b:0;}i:3948;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3948";s:4:"NAME";s:23:"Psychology Consultation";s:4:"CODE";s:23:"psychology-consultation";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:0:"";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:2310:"<p>
	 Unstable emotions, anxiety and depression often cause psychological discomfort and may negatively affect your health condition. Psychological problems may prevent your desired pregnancy or&nbsp;overshadow the excitement of&nbsp;a&nbsp;new baby.
</p>
<p>
	 Psychological counseling may be&nbsp;wanted in&nbsp;different life situations but it&nbsp;is&nbsp;invaluable in&nbsp;the cases of&nbsp;infertility, recurrent pregnancy loss, difficult pregnancy or&nbsp;its termination, postpartum depression. Our psychologist will help you to&nbsp;recognize the problem, understand its reasons and find a&nbsp;solution suitable for you.
</p>
<p>
	 During the consultation, please, be&nbsp;prepared to&nbsp;answer questions and do&nbsp;some tests. You might be&nbsp;asked to&nbsp;describe your relationship with your partner, your fears and anxieties, your worries and your expectations. The effectiveness of&nbsp;the consultation will depend not only on&nbsp;our specialist’s experience, qualification and communications skills. Your own willingness to&nbsp;be&nbsp;open and sincere, to&nbsp;cooperate and follow the advice is&nbsp;also very important. Sometimes only one consultation proves sufficient, in&nbsp;other cases several meetings will be&nbsp;required to&nbsp;help you cope with a&nbsp;difficult situation. Much will depend on&nbsp;your condition and your needs.
</p>
<p>
	 You may want to&nbsp;make an&nbsp;appointment with our psychologist yourself or&nbsp;one of&nbsp;our doctors (an&nbsp;<a href="/services/consultations/internal-medicine-consultation/">internist</a>, a&nbsp;<a href="/services/consultations/gynecological-consultation/">gynecologist</a>, a&nbsp;<a href="/services/consultations/urology-consultation/">urologist</a> or&nbsp;a&nbsp;<a href="/services/consultations/fertility-specialist-consultation/">fertility specialist</a>) may refer you for psychological consultation. Please, make a&nbsp;call or&nbsp;use our <a href="#contactus" data-modal-open="">contact form</a>. We&nbsp;will get back to&nbsp;you to&nbsp;offer convenient date and time.
</p>
<p>
	 In&nbsp;addition, you have an&nbsp;opportunity to&nbsp;get an&nbsp;online consultation. However, please, remember that an&nbsp;online consultation cannot be&nbsp;equal to&nbsp;actually seeing a&nbsp;doctor.
