RIPTION";s:3031:"&lt;p&gt;
	ICRM doctors help infertile couples to&nbsp;become parents with the help of&nbsp;egg donation, embryo adoption and surrogacy programs. Our patients can suggest their own candidate to&nbsp;an&nbsp;egg donor and a&nbsp;surrogate mother, or&nbsp;select one from our bank.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Egg donation IVF program&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	The program is&nbsp;offered to&nbsp;those patients who do&nbsp;not have their own oocytes (due to&nbsp;premature ovarian failure, removal of&nbsp;the ovaries in&nbsp;the history or&nbsp;menopause), who have too few eggs and for this reason good embryos cannot be&nbsp;made in&nbsp;IVF cycles, or&nbsp;if&nbsp;a&nbsp;woman has a&nbsp;hereditary disease. Here are the stages of&nbsp;the treatment program:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;pre-treatment examination and tests for a&nbsp;recipient (a&nbsp;woman who has problems with oocytes) and an&nbsp;egg donor;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;IVF/ICSI treatment program that includes hormonal stimulation of&nbsp;the donor’s ovaries and preparation of&nbsp;the recipient’s endometrium for embryo transfer;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;fertilization of&nbsp;the donor’s eggs retrieved at&nbsp;the follicular puncture with the sperm of&nbsp;the recipient’s partner or&nbsp;donor in&nbsp;the laboratory;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;embryo culture;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;embryo transfer to&nbsp;the prepared womb of&nbsp;the recipient;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;post-transfer support with medications;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;pregnancy testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	If&nbsp;frozen donor eggs are used, some of&nbsp;the stages are skipped&nbsp;— donor eggs will just be&nbsp;thawed when necessary and fertilized, then the best embryos will be&nbsp;transferred to&nbsp;the recipient’s uterine cavity.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Embryo donation IVF treatment program&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	In&nbsp;IVF protocols with the embryos made of&nbsp;donor eggs and donor sperm, both fresh and frozen biological material can be&nbsp;used (but only frozen donor sperm). If&nbsp;fresh oocytes are used, the following stages will be&nbsp;completed before the embryo transfer and pregnancy testing:
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;pre-treatment examination and tests for a&nbsp;recipient and a&nbsp;donor;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;eggs retrieval by&nbsp;means of&nbsp;hormonal stimulation of&nbsp;the donor’s ovaries and her follicle puncture;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;donor eggs fertilization by&nbsp;donor sperm followed by&nbsp;embryo culture;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;preparation of&nbsp;the recipient’s uterine lining.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
	In&nbsp;the case of&nbsp;frozen donor eggs, the protocol will be&nbsp;much shorter&nbsp;— it&nbsp;will only be&nbsp;necessary to&nbsp;prepare the endometrium of&nbsp;the future mother, to&nbsp;thaw the embryo when it&nbsp;is&nbsp;necessary and transfer it&nbsp;into her womb. In&nbsp;ICRM, we&nbsp;offer PGT-tested and recommended for transfer embryos for adoption.
&lt;/p&gt;";s:13:"actions_count";i:0;s:10:"prices_url";s:51:"/prices-and-actions/prices/#donorship-and-surrogacy";s:7:"picture";a:10:{s:8:"ORIGINAL";s:28:"/upload/iblock/dca/donor.png";s:13:"webp_ORIGINAL";s:51:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/dca/0_0_1_95/donor.webp";s:12:"main_complex";s:28:"/upload/iblock/dca/donor.png";s:17:"webp_main_complex";s:55:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/dca/114_114_1_95/donor.webp";s:14:"services_index";s:28:"/upload/iblock/dca/donor.png";s:19:"webp_services_index";s:55:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/dca/114_114_1_95/donor.webp";s:8:"category";s:28:"/upload/iblock/dca/donor.png";s:13:"webp_category";s:55:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/dca/114_114_1_95/donor.webp";s:6:"prices";s:28:"/upload/iblock/dca/donor.png";s:11:"webp_prices";s:55:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/dca/114_114_1_95/donor.webp";}s:24:"showServiceTypesOnPrices";b:0;s:8:"services";a:8:{i:3961;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3961";s:4:"NAME";s:27:"IVF with Your Own Egg Donor";s:4:"CODE";s:27:"ivf-with-your-own-egg-donor";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:0:"";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:447:"<p>
	 The final decision about the candidate will be&nbsp;made by&nbsp;your fertility specialist based on&nbsp;the potential donor’s examination results.
</p>
<p>
	 All costs for examination of&nbsp;the egg donor, her preparation for the treatment program, her medications, ultrasound scans and other IVF procedures must be&nbsp;covered by&nbsp;the patient (recipient).
</p>
<p>
	 IVF with an&nbsp;egg donor includes several stages:
</p>";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:62:"/services/donorship-and-surrogacy/ivf-with-your-own-egg-donor/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"186";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:652:"&lt;p&gt;If&nbsp;a&nbsp;patient does not have her own eggs or&nbsp;they are of&nbsp;low quality, or&nbsp;if&nbsp;a&nbsp;patient has a&nbsp;hereditary disease, IVF with donor eggs may be&nbsp;recommended. A&nbsp;patient may suggest her own candidate (in&nbsp;this case she will be&nbsp;a&nbsp;non-anonymous donor) who must meet the following requirements:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;be&nbsp;over 18&nbsp;and under&nbsp;35;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;be&nbsp;mentally and physically healthy;&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;do&nbsp;all required genetic tests to&nbsp;prevent inheritance of&nbsp;birth defects and hereditary diseases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}s:31:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:428";s:21:"PROPERTY_STAGES_VALUE";a:6:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:123:"Ultrasound monitoring of&nbsp;the follicles growth in&nbsp;the donor and the uterine lining condition in&nbsp;the recipient";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:1;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:77:"Ovarian puncture and eggs retrieval from the donor (under general anesthesia)";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:2;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:41:"Eggs fertilization in&nbsp;the laboratory";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:3;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:14:"Embryo culture";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:4;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:75:"Transfer of&nbsp;1-2 embryo(s) to&nbsp;the recipient&rsquo;s uterine cavity";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}i:5;a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:17:"Pregnancy testing";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}}s:26:"PROPERTY_SPECIALISTS_VALUE";a:7:{i:0;s:2:"50";i:1;s:2:"28";i:2;s:2:"63";i:3;s:2:"65";i:4;s:1:"4";i:5;s:2:"55";i:6;s:2:"10";}s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE";s:11:"179 000 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:431";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";s:28:"Medications are not included";s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:432";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:433";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:434";s:23:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE";N;s:26:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:435";s:29:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE";s:1:"1";s:32:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:436";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:437";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:438";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:591";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:592";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3961:593";s:28:"PROPERTY