<p>
	 Candidates to&nbsp;sperm donors are thoroughly selected before they are included into our bank. To&nbsp;choose the healthiest men, our specialists check their physical parameters, lab test results and semen parameters. We&nbsp;guarantee that our donor sperm samples meet the following requirements:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>sufficient number of&nbsp;motile, active sperm cells;</li>
	<li>high quality of&nbsp;sperm&nbsp;— the gametes are morphologically normal, without any defects;</li>
	<li>sufficient volume of&nbsp;ejaculate for several IVF procedures.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	 In&nbsp;order to&nbsp;prevent transferring to&nbsp;a&nbsp;patient such infections as&nbsp;syphilis, HIV, hepatitis&nbsp;B and&nbsp;C, we&nbsp;only use frozen sperm after a&nbsp;6-month quarantine, during which a&nbsp;donor is&nbsp;tested several times for the infections with negative results.
</p>
<h2>How to&nbsp;choose an&nbsp;egg or&nbsp;a&nbsp;sperm donor?</h2>
<p>
	 After discussing your treatment program with our doctor you can see the profiles of&nbsp;our donors using our website from. You can choose a&nbsp;donor based on&nbsp;your preferences taking into consideration his/her appearance, blood group and&nbsp;Rh factor, and other characteristics from the donor’s profile. IVF treatment programs with donor eggs or&nbsp;sperm from the ICRM cryobank are anonymous. IVF programs with donor gametes (eggs, sperm) have high success rates up&nbsp;to&nbsp;60% and higher. The ICRM doctors can help every couple to&nbsp;achieve pregnancy and give birth to&nbsp;a&nbsp;healthy child.
</p>";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:46:"/services/donorship-and-surrogacy/donor-sperm/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"186";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:407:"&lt;p&gt;In&nbsp;the cases of&nbsp;confirmed absolute male factor infertility, the couple can use donor sperm from the ICRM cryobank. Donor sperm may also be&nbsp;suggested if&nbsp;previous IVF attempts failed or&nbsp;if&nbsp;a&nbsp;male partner has hereditary disorders. Donor sperm cells are also necessary for single women who would like to&nbsp;get pregnant and give birth to&nbsp;a&nbsp;baby.&lt;/p&gt;";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}s:31:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:428";s:21:"PROPERTY_STAGES_VALUE";a:0:{}s:26:"PROPERTY_SPECIALISTS_VALUE";a:0:{}s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE";s:10:"17 500 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:431";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:432";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:433";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:434";s:23:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE";N;s:26:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:435";s:29:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE";N;s:32:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:436";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:437";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:438";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:591";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:592";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:593";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:594";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3964:595";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE3