<p>
	 In&nbsp;the ICRM cryobank, we&nbsp;have donor embryos made by&nbsp;means of&nbsp;fertilization of&nbsp;donor eggs with donor sperm. Here are the advantages of&nbsp;using donor embryos:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>all donors went through thorough selection process, they are physically and mentally healthy, their biomaterial is&nbsp;of&nbsp;high quality;</li>
	<li>you have a&nbsp;possibility to&nbsp;choose donors based on&nbsp;their phenotypic characteristics;</li>
	<li>many donor embryos are genetically tested and have normal chromosomal structure;</li>
	<li>the survival rate of&nbsp;vitrified (frozen) donor embryos after thawing is&nbsp;very high&nbsp;— 99%, that is&nbsp;why the success rate in&nbsp;donor embryo IVF cycles is&nbsp;the same as&nbsp;in&nbsp;«fresh» cycles;</li>
	<li>lower price of&nbsp;the IVF protocol compared to&nbsp;the standard one because the most expensive stages were performed before fertilization of&nbsp;donor eggs with donor sperm.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	 A&nbsp;donor embryo is&nbsp;a&nbsp;chance for infertile couples to&nbsp;give birth to&nbsp;a&nbsp;long awaited baby.
</p>";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:61:"/services/donorship-and-surrogacy/donor-embryo-without-pgt-a/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"186";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:617:"&lt;p&gt;In&nbsp;the case partners do&nbsp;not have their own quality gametes or&nbsp;if&nbsp;there is&nbsp;a&nbsp;high risk of&nbsp;inheriting a&nbsp;serious disease by&nbsp;a&nbsp;future baby, doctors can suggest using donor embryo(s) for IVF. The procedure is&nbsp;easier for a&nbsp;woman than a&nbsp;standard IVF protocol because hormonal ovarian stimulation and surgical intervention for her own oocytes retrieval will not be&nbsp;necessary. However, a&nbsp;woman or&nbsp;a&nbsp;couple must be&nbsp;psychologically prepared to&nbsp;the fact that their baby will be&nbsp;genetically different from them.&lt;/p&gt;";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}s:31:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:428";s:21:"PROPERTY_STAGES_VALUE";a:0:{}s:26:"PROPERTY_SPECIALISTS_VALUE";a:0:{}s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE";s:10:"70 000 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:431";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:432";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:433";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:434";s:23:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE";N;s:26:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:435";s:29:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE";N;s:32:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:436";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:437";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:438";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:591";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3965:592";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_V