	 PGT-A, a&nbsp;pre-implantation testing for aneuploidies, is&nbsp;performed to&nbsp;reduce probability of&nbsp;IVF failure. It&nbsp;identifies chromosomally abnormal embryos that may lead to&nbsp;Down, Edwards’, Patau’s and other common disorders resulting in&nbsp;implantation failures or&nbsp;miscarriages at&nbsp;early stages of&nbsp;pregnancy (up&nbsp;to&nbsp;12&nbsp;weeks). The advantage of&nbsp;the technique is&nbsp;better detection of&nbsp;mosaicism&nbsp;— two or&nbsp;more cell lines with different genotypes in&nbsp;one embryo. Unlike aneuploidies, mosaicism does not seem to&nbsp;depend on&nbsp;a&nbsp;female’s age.
</p>
<p>
	 In&nbsp;ICRM, PGT-A is&nbsp;performed using NGS method. The test allows transferring an&nbsp;embryo with lower risk of&nbsp;chromosomal disorders into the uterine cavity.
</p>";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:40:"/services/genetic-tests/pgt-a-using-ngs/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"185";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:397:"&lt;p&gt;According to&nbsp;the WHO data, women over 35&nbsp;are at&nbsp;higher risk of&nbsp;giving birth to&nbsp;a baby with chromosomal disorders. Aneuploidy is&nbsp;a&nbsp;wrong number of&nbsp;chromosomes. The defect occurs due to&nbsp;a&nbsp;mistake at&nbsp;the stage of&nbsp;meiosis and often causes spontaneous miscarriages, especially in&nbsp;the first trimester of&nbsp;pregnancy.&lt;/p&gt;";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}s:31:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:428";s:21:"PROPERTY_STAGES_VALUE";a:0:{}s:26:"PROPERTY_SPECIALISTS_VALUE";a:1:{i:0;s:2:"11";}s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:431";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:432";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE";s:10:"32 000 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:433";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";s:7:"30 days";s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:434";s:23:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE";N;s:26:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:435";s:29:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE";N;s:32:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:436";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:437";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:438";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:591";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:592";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:593";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:594";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3954:595";s:33:"PROPER