Comparing this endoscopic technique with a classic abdominal operation, after laparoscopy the patient:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;feels less pain;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;loses very little blood;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;can stand up 2-3 hours after the operation and go back to normal physical activities by the end of the 24-hour period;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;in few months, can hardly find the scars on the skin.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
