s:20:"PROPERTY_PRICE_VALUE";s:6:"69 000";s:23:"PROPERTY_PRICE_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4500:439";s:32:"PROPERTY_PRICE_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";s:38:"intravenous anesthesia is not included";s:35:"PROPERTY_PRICE_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4500:440";s:4:"SORT";s:3:"120";s:17:"PREVIEW_TEXT_TYPE";s:4:"html";}s:20:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'languageAccessors";a:0:{}s:7:"related";a:0:{}s:9:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'hidden";a:0:{}s:10:"'.chr(0).'*'.chr(0).'visible";a:0:{}}}}s:6:"action";b:0;}i:4027;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"4027";s:4:"NAME";s:15:"Anesthesia Care";s:4:"CODE";s:15:"anesthesia-care";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:42:"Pain control during surgical interventions";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:1386:"<p>
	Correct anesthesia ensures the following:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>total loss of&nbsp;sensation;</li>
	<li>postanesthetic recovery to&nbsp;full consciousness in&nbsp;average about 10&nbsp;minutes after the operation;</li>
	<li>high tolerability to&nbsp;the medications used for anesthesia.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	In&nbsp;our Centre, experienced highly-qualified anaesthesiologists-resuscitators will perform anesthesia depending on&nbsp;the type of&nbsp;your surgery, your medical indications and history:
</p>
<ul>
	<li>intravenous anesthesia of&nbsp;the 1st and 2nd category of&nbsp;difficulty;</li>
	<li>general anesthesia with artificial lung ventilation of&nbsp;the 1st and 2nd degree of&nbsp;difficulty;</li>
	<li>epidural anesthesia;</li>
	<li>general anesthesia with artificial lung ventilation + epidural anesthesia;</li>
	<li>local anesthesia;</li>
	<li>monitored anesthesia care (conscious sedation);</li>
	<li>intravenous anesthesia for follicular puncture.</li>
</ul>
<p>
	In&nbsp;addition, if&nbsp;necessary, our doctors will perform one-group blood transfusion, plasma transfusion, anesthesia prolongation if&nbsp;the operation is&nbsp;long. The extensive experience of&nbsp;our anesthesiologists, up-to-date artificial lung ventilator and other medical equipment will ensure high effectiveness and safety of&nbsp;anesthesia during your surgical procedure.
</p>";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:47:"/services/reproductive-surgery/anesthesia-care/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"183";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";a:2:{s:4:"TEXT";s:518:"&lt;p&gt;The role of&nbsp;an&nbsp;anaesthesiologist-resuscitator is&nbsp;much bigger than just ensure that patients do&nbsp;not feel any pain during surgery or&nbsp;any painful manipulations. The specialist provides a&nbsp;package of&nbsp;measures aimed at&nbsp;prevention of&nbsp;operational trauma, safe support of&nbsp;a&nbsp;patient&rsquo;s vital functions during the operation and after&nbsp;it. The doctor must monitor a&nbsp;patient&rsquo;s condition throughout the surgery until his/her wake&nbsp;up.&lt;/p&gt;";s:4:"TYPE";s:4:"HTML";}s:31:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:428";s:21:"PROPERTY_STAGES_VALUE";a:0:{}s:26:"PROPERTY_SPECIALISTS_VALUE";a:0:{}s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE";s:14:"from 1 000 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:431";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:432";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:433";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:434";s:23:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE";N;s:26:"PROPERTY_CURRENCY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:435";s:29:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE";N;s:32:"PROPERTY_SHOW_ON_PRICES_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:436";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:437";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:438";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:591";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE";N;s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:592";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";N;s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE4_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"4027:593";s:28:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_ACTION_VALUE";N;s:31:"PROPERTY_PRICE3_ACTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"402