&lt;p&gt;Ultrasound examination is&nbsp;a&nbsp;non-invasive method aimed to&nbsp;assess the condition of&nbsp;internal organs and systems of&nbsp;organs. The main advantages of&nbsp;ultrasound are its safety and high informative value. Based on&nbsp;ultrasound findings, our specialists can:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;verify a&nbsp;diagnosis;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;reveal hidden pathology in&nbsp;asymptomatic patients;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;clarify the cause of&nbsp;infertility;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;evaluate health condition of&nbsp;future mother and father before planning an&nbsp;IVF program, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During family planning and pregnancy, ultrasound is&nbsp;used to&nbsp;monitor ovulation, to&nbsp;find out the date of&nbsp;conception and pregnancy term, to&nbsp;follow the fetus development, to&nbsp;reveal intrauterine defects, and at&nbsp;the late pregnancy period&nbsp;&mdash; to&nbsp;see the baby&rsquo;s position for better management of&nbsp;labor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Advantages of&nbsp;ultrasound examination method&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pros of&nbsp;ultrasound screening:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;performed in&nbsp;real-time mode;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;an&nbsp;area to&nbsp;be&nbsp;examined can easily be&nbsp;changed;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;the plan of&nbsp;monitoring can be&nbsp;corrected depending on&nbsp;the current situation;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;image magnification and detailed study of&nbsp;zones of&nbsp;special interest are&nbsp;possible when necessary.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In&nbsp;our International Centre for reproductive Medicine, the following ultrasound examinations are available:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;pelvic ultrasound;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;breast ultrasound;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;scrotal ultrasound;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;kidneys and urinary bladder ultrasound;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;prostate ultrasound;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;abdominal ultrasound;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;thyroid ultrasound;&lt;/li&gt;
   &lt;li&gt;soft tissues ultrasound.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In&nbsp;addition, we&nbsp;offer ultrasound monitoring of&nbsp;ovulation. For pelvic ultrasound both abdominal and vaginal transducers are used.&lt;/p&gt;";s:13:"actions_count";i:0;s:10:"prices_url";s:51:"/prices-and-actions/prices/#ultrasound-examinations";s:7:"picture";a:10:{s:8:"ORIGINAL";s:26:"/upload/iblock/0cc/uzi.png";s:13:"webp_ORIGINAL";s:49:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/0cc/0_0_1_95/uzi.webp";s:12:"main_complex";s:26:"/upload/iblock/0cc/uzi.png";s:17:"webp_main_complex";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/0cc/114_114_1_95/uzi.webp";s:14:"services_index";s:26:"/upload/iblock/0cc/uzi.png";s:19:"webp_services_index";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/0cc/114_114_1_95/uzi.webp";s:8:"category";s:26:"/upload/iblock/0cc/uzi.png";s:13:"webp_category";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/0cc/114_114_1_95/uzi.webp";s:6:"prices";s:26:"/upload/iblock/0cc/uzi.png";s:11:"webp_prices";s:53:"/upload/resize_cache/iblock/0cc/114_114_1_95/uzi.webp";}s:24:"showServiceTypesOnPrices";b:0;s:8:"services";a:11:{i:3972;a:86:{s:2:"ID";s:4:"3972";s:4:"NAME";s:17:"Pelvic Ultrasound";s:4:"CODE";s:17:"pelvic-ultrasound";s:12:"PREVIEW_TEXT";s:37:"With abdominal and vaginal transducer";s:11:"DETAIL_TEXT";s:0:"";s:15:"DETAIL_PAGE_URL";s:52:"/services/ultrasound-examinations/pelvic-ultrasound/";s:17:"IBLOCK_SECTION_ID";s:3:"181";s:9:"IBLOCK_ID";s:2:"90";s:28:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE";b:0;s:31:"PROPERTY_PARTICULARITY_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3972:428";s:21:"PROPERTY_STAGES_VALUE";a:0:{}s:26:"PROPERTY_SPECIALISTS_VALUE";a:0:{}s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE";s:9:"2 300 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3972:431";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";s:25:"with abdominal transducer";s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE1_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3972:432";s:26:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE";s:9:"2 500 ₽";s:29:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_FULL_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3972:433";s:33:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE";s:23:"with vaginal transducer";s:36:"PROPERTY_PRICE2_DESCRIPTION_VALUE_ID";s:8:"3972:434";s:23:"PROPERTY_